---
title: Florentine Stuffed Portobellos with Spinach & Sun-Dried Tomato
description: Who doesn't love a creamy, luscious spinach dip? We've added both thyme-roasted and sun-dried tomatoes to the equation for a double whammy of flavor. Stuffed inside meaty Portobellos and served on a bed of fluffy rice, we know you'll be craving this dish again!
